features: WHAT YOU GET: 80 sheets of Christmas letter paper are included in the package, enough for your crafting and greeting needs.

FESTIVE DESIGNS: Patterned with colorful light bulbs at 4 borders, and printed with word Merry Christmas on the top, delicate and elegant, great writing paper to give your warm greetings to your friends.

PROPER SIZE: Each sheet measures 21.6 x 28 cm/8.5 x 11 inch, and the letterhead leaves enough blank sections for you to write your best wishes and greetings, which is very thoughtful. Dimensions are measured manually, please allow for errors.
DURABLE MATERIAL: Our writing paper is made of good quality paper, the paper is textured, durable and reliable, with clear patterns and smooth writing, and can be used for printing.

WIDE APPLICATION: Perfect for letters, greeting cards, party invitations, office supplies, school supplies, suitable for everyone, especially teenagers. They are wonderful letterheads to send to your family, friends, and even Santa Claus.

reviews.reviewText: This product b was more for writing a handwritten Christmas letter. I needed it to run 200 Christmas letters on, and thought the design was only on one side. The design was two sided. I made it work, but prefer a one sided sturdier paper for running off our Christmas letter.
